spec_data.Name: neXtaw
spec_data.Description:
neXtaw is a replacement library for the Athena (libXaw) widget set. It
is based on Xaw3d, by Kaleb Keithley and is almost 100% backward
compatible with it. Its goal is to try to emulate the look and feel of
the N*XTSTEP GUI.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 04 Aug 2017 07:44:49 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Modified version of the Athena Widgets with N*XTSTEP appearance
